metadata.name: Simian Samurai's
metadata.description: "Simian Samurai's" NFT collection features a stunning lineup of highly detailed and beautifully designed samurai-themed apes, orangutans, chimpanzees, and gorillas. Each NFT is a unique piece of artwork that captures the essence of traditional Japanese samurai culture and martial arts, combined with the strength and intelligence of our simian subjects. Whether you're a collector, trader, or fan of martial arts-inspired art, these NFTs offer exceptional value and a one-of-a-kind addition to any digital art collection. Additionally, a portion of the proceeds from the sale of each NFT will go towards wildlife conservation efforts, making "Simian Samurai's" NFTs both a beautiful and ethical choice for art lovers and crypto enthusiasts alike.
